fields.Microsoft.VSTS.TCM.ReproSteps:
1. Create an engagement
  2. Upload TB
  3. Setup MA, PAP, (GATs) to generate RAs
  4. Generate TOD wp (e.g. REV.P02.d2)
  5. Upload DIF and mark in use a dataset
  6. Open the wp in edit mode
  7. Select a dataset
  8. Select Audit sampling at Testing approach
  9. Select Attribute at Determine the sample type
  10. Select a response at Select the Number of Expected Deviations
  11. Select  a response at Control reliance approach
  12. Select  a method at Determine the sample method
  13. Select Variable at Determine the sample type
  14. Select  a response at Select the population subject to sampling
  15. Save the wp
  16. Observe
